room_title: Escape room "Speakeasy" by Escape It Grandview in Columbus
room_description: Sitting adjacent to the La Tavola restaurant and literally in its shadow, Escape It is nestled snuggly in the heart of Grandview Heights. When visitors locate the lower space, they're in for an adventure. Specifically, a room-escape game adventure, filled with twists, turns, and plenty of clues to solve.
